entries.femaleVariant: What do you think about all this?
Whaddaya think? All that's going on?
You in charge of the clan now?
So, what? you're at the helm of the clan now?
OK, how d'you wanna do this?
entries.maleVariant: OK, how you wanna do this?

entries.femaleVariant: Mitch is already setting up the recon. You'll sneak into the Wraiths' camp while I cover you.
They found an abandoned cement plant to squat in. With a mass of heavy gear.
Locusts would be a better name for them. They fly into a place, strip it of all it's got, then move on. But this time…
Do you see the wall? They've added some primitive security measures.
Tire tracks. Their vehicles were moving heavy freight.
If they haven't scrapped and gutted the place for parts, you could access the local cam-net. You would just need to find the control room.
The main building, there. Saul must be inside.
That's probably the one they kept Saul in.
Is everything clear?
Quietly. An open assault would be suicide.
[End recon] Got somethin' to work with now.
Well I'll be... Panam and V. What's going on there?
Hey, Panam! Seriously? You really aim to do this?
Yeah, let's go get Saul.
Let's resummarize?
Let's sum things up, just to be sure.
Yeah, 'course.
Perfect. Mitch, is the van primed?
Going on my own. See you there.
OK, you take the wheel.
OK, just don't lose your way. Time is not our friend on this.
The skywalk – it connects the garage to the main structure.
That guard post is probably connected to the rest of the camp.
What are our chances?
Not a fan of waiting, huh?
How do ya see our chances?
Looks like someone doesn't enjoy waiting patiently.
entries.maleVariant: Looks like someone doesn't enjoy waitin' patiently.

entries.femaleVariant: It points to them aiming to stay longer. The question is why. Who knows for sure, but I would guess that Saul is part of the reason.
If he's still there, we have to find a way inside.
Maybe, but there are also breaches in the wall, lightly guarded sections…
Our way in?
Quite a spread... Be like looking for a diamond in a hailstorm.
It could have been equipment... Either that or Saul's not their only prisoner.
Goin' alone. Meet you there.
Yeah, 'course I'm going with you.
Want me drivin'?
Yep, I need to fiddle with my scope a bit.
V, it's good you're here.
We're chooms, that's why.
Nomads should help one another.
You can. Just not for free.
I could help you out.
There's a "but" attached to that.
Not for free.
I might have guessed. There never is anything free with you statics.
Fine. I will give you one of the best sniper rifles on the West Coast.
Belonged to a nomad family too once. City doesn't change us all that much, I guess.
That's hard to deny.
Always, Panam. You and me're chooms. Thought that was clear.
Careful, or I'll start believing that. You won't be able to get rid of me.
I'll survive, I'm sure.
What happened? Spit it out.
The Wraiths took Saul.
The brickbrain ventured out with a small patrol and never came back.
Sure it was Wraiths?
We've been observing their camp. We know they're holding prisoners, including someone important.
I don't know why but... I felt I could count on you.
What happened?
Back with the Aldecaldos?
Had no idea you and the Aldecaldos had made up.
They continue to grind my gears something terrible.
But... y'know…
They're family.
Exactly.
Whatever goodwill you might feel, I'm sure you won't turn down one of the best sniper rifles on the West Coast.
That and the gratitude of the 'Caldos.
Sounds fancy.
Once you have it in hand, "fancy" all of a sudden becomes "kickass."
Let's go. Mitch will walk you through the details.
Where's Mitch? He was supposed to meet me here.
He'll be here any minute.
Huh, you never mentioned seeking outside help.
Leader got abducted and you're not about to do anything?
Leader gets nabbed and you, what? Hope for the best?
entries.maleVariant: Your leader gets nabbed and you, what, hope for the best?

entries.femaleVariant: Rather not think about what you'd do for the ones at the bottom of your food chain.
You're asking for trouble…
Leave it. She has a right not to understand.
entries.maleVariant: Leave it. He has a right not to understand.

entries.femaleVariant: Look around! The last attacks left barely half of us standing! Our supplies are stuck outside goddamn Reno. And our gear... don't get me started!
I floated a drone over the Wraiths' camp.
[Take shard] Lemme see.
Yep, let's go get Saul.
I did what I could. Take a tour.
How are you?
Mitch, how ya been?
Let's see what we got here.
We're up shit creek, static. And I don't know if we're ever going to find or fashion a paddle, try as we might.
We have live eyes on it. Will you take a look?
Hey there, V.
Mhm. We wait and gather our strength.
Just us two? What about the rest?!
Do it quiet, sure. Perfect for two.
Wait, meanin' it's just gonna be us two?
Ah, goin' in quiet. Two's all you need.
entries.maleVariant: Goin' in quiet. Two's all you need.

entries.femaleVariant: What about all you guys?!
So we do what Saul would want us to do.
It's not that I don't want to go, to serve some Raffens up some justice! It's just…
Solid job.
We need to free Saul.
We can use all the help we can get.
[Lean on car] How we doin' this?
[Lean on car] Some kind of problem?
There a problem?
Just that if we're looking outside, we must be a hot mess inside.
That's why we'll go in quiet. A frontal assault would be suicide.
Mitch is already setting up recon. V will sneak into the Wraiths' camp, while I'll be her guardian rifle.
entries.maleVariant: Mitch is already setting up recon. V will sneak into the Wraiths' camp, while I'll be his guardian rifle.

entries.femaleVariant: There's Mitch.
And hey, it shouldn't be me occupyin' your thoughts, but Saul.
My stint in Mexico taught me there's no hole you can't crawl out of.
Something you'd like to say?
But when the clan's decided, it's decided. That's the way things are. I dunno... maybe it'll be our own undoing.
Y'know, we could use a war vet's expertise. Sure you're stayin' back?
We are the cavalry riding to the rescue, hoping to make it in time.
You will strive to slip into the camp while I cover you. But we’ll let bullets fly only as a last resort.
They are many, we are few. So we'll need to look for any chance to gain the upper hand.
A Techtronika "Grad" – you saw it in action already.
A Techtronika "Grad" – you saw it in action already. All yours, compliments of the 'Caldos.
Wishing duct tape could right all the world's wrongs.
I floated a drone over the Wraiths' camp.
Will you take a look or would you rather keep mouthing off?
OK, got some stuff to work with now.
Sheesh… OK. The Raffens captured Saul. They're holding him somewhere inside their base.
You will pull Saul out, and the three of us will ride away at top speed. All clear now?
Someone has to...
You know you have a piston missing, right?
Someone has to!
Ignore that.
Hold on a minute, I got one more thing.
If you find Saul hasn't flatlined, you'll probably need this.
[Take SuperJet] Sure hope so.
V, will you ride with me?
I mostly improvised, actually.
Either way, it'll have to do.
Hope so. Doubt I could carry him on my back.
entries.maleVariant: Hope so. Doubt I could carry him out on my back.

entries.femaleVariant: Spiked SuperJet. A rhino dose. It should speed up Saul's central pump.
So, that should be everything.
The Raffens can't see it – active camo. But that practically inhales battery juice, so make it quick.
Do you see the tracks?
The tracks lead to the truck. Can you scan it?
I'm sure every passing second puts Saul another step closer to death's door.
Go on, V. Get him outta there.
I was helpin' Mitch with the drones, and truth be told... it doesn't look good.
Those parasites knew just where and how to hunker down.
Just curious. Looks like you're in charge of the camp with Saul gone.
I simply have the loudest opinions. And just so happens most folks tend to agree with them.
But I'd like to be clear. What you and Panam aim to do... I'm grateful.
Even if your plan has little chance of succeeding.
Aren't you the optimist.
A realist.
But good luck all the same. Try not to die.
You taking a look or not?
Guess probably for Saul...
Saul.
You want my two ennies? Without him... all this comes unglued.
But to do that, sure helps havin' a guidin' hand – if ya catch my meanin'.
Heh... I'd rather move my ass than sit on it, that's for damn sure.
If you wanna know my take, I think Panam's right. In and out quietly's our best bet.
Her? After what happened to Scorpion, she shows up here?
entries.maleVariant: Him? After what happened to Scorpion, he shows up here?
